==German==

===Etymology===
The greeting evolved from the commoners’ greeting (said to lords) ''servus humillimus (Domine spectabilis)'', meaning ''your humble servant, my noble Lord''. No [[subservience]] is implied in modern use.

===Pronunciation===
*{{IPA|/ˈzɛːrvus/}}

===Interjection===
'''servus'''

# [[hello]], [[hi]]

